</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The adjacency matrix of an undirected simple graph is <a href=3D"https:/=
/en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Symmetric_matrix" title=3D"Symmetric matrix">symmetr=
