/span> is the first eigenvalue of <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"fon=
t-style:italic;">A</span> for the vector <span class=3D"texhtml"><span clas=
s=3D"nowrap"><i>v</i> =3D (1, ..., 1)</span></span> (it is easy to check th=
at it is an eigenvalue and it is the maximum because of the above bound). T=
he multiplicity of this eigenvalue is the number of connected components of=
 <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">G</span>, in par=
